quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  8,9,"Recall: youpl crying for help from your Lord, so He responded to you, “I am surely reinforcing you with one thousand angels in succession1 .”"
  8,10,"And Allah only made it as a glad tiding, and so that your hearts should become serene thereby, for support1is only from Allah; indeed, Allah is Almighty, All-Wise."